This version includes revisions to concept land use since 2002 based on adopted plans, ground conditions, and correction of errors found in original data.</abstract>       <purpose>Represents generalized areas where development and redevelopment ('Areas Of Change') are planned within the City and County of Denver, as identified in the plan "Blueprint Denver, An Integrated Land Use and Transportation Plan."   </purpose>       <supplinf>Built from original Area of Change (AOC) Version, corrected based on adopted plans, ground conditions, errors found in original data, and snapped to revised parcels and street centerlines.</supplinf>     </descript>     <status>       <progress>In work</progress>       <update>As needed</update>     </status>     <spdom>       <bounding>         <westbc>-105.055587</westbc>         <eastbc>-104.734523</eastbc>         <northbc>39.830904</northbc>         <southbc>39.624170</southbc>       </bounding>     </spdom>     <keywords>       <theme>         <themekt>None</themekt>         <themekey>planning</themekey>       </theme>       <theme>         <themekt>ISO 19115 Topic Categories</themekt>         <themekey>boundaries</themekey>         <themekey>planningCadastre</themekey>       </theme>       <place>         <placekt>None</placekt>         <placekey>Denver</placekey>         <placekey>Denver County</placekey>         <placekey>Colorado</placekey>         <placekey>USA</placekey>       </place>     </keywords>     <accconst>None</accconst>     <useconst>ACCESS CONSTRAINTS:   None.
